The project has 4 functions:

1. Book a Room
2. Modify a booking
3. Delete a booking
4. Search for records by Phone Number/Name

The C++ program creates "CBSEH.dat" file and uses it to store hotel records.
The Source code is available in the file "hotel.cpp".
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The Hotel Management System Project Source Code (hotel.cpp) requires the TURBO C++ compiler on the Windows Operating System inorder to compile and run.

1.Install Turbo C++ Compiler
2.Place a copy of the hotel.cpp file in the bin folder of TURBOC3
3.Create a file named CBSEH.dat by opening notepad and saving the empty notepad file with file name "CBSEH.dat"
4.Open Turbo C++ and run hotel.cpp
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
